OL,7,FAn asylum seeker who allegedly
OL,8,Fprofessed to be the Prophet Muhammad
OL,9,Fand threatened to get a knife to kill
OL,10,Fsomeone in Belfast has been jailed for
OL,11,Fthree months.
OL,13,FProsecutors said Zakariya Hurre made
OL,14,Fstabbing gestures at members of the
OL,15,Fpublic before fleeing through the city
OL,16,Fcentre in a bid to evade police.
OL,18,FThe 28-year-old Somalian, who claims
OL,19,Fhe was only rapping on the streets,
OL,20,Fadmitted a charge of disorderly
OL,21,Fbehaviour.
