OL,7,FBelfast Magistrates' Court heard
OL,8,Fpolice received complaints about a man
OL,9,Fstriking out at passers-by on July 11
OL,10,Fthis year.
OL,12,F"One witness claimed the defendant
OL,13,Fstated he was the Prophet Muhammad and
OL,14,Fthat he was going to get a knife and
OL,15,Fkill someone," a Crown lawyer said.
OL,17,F"He was gesturing with his hands in a
OL,18,Fstabbing motion."
