OL,7,FWhen officers detained Hurre on Lower
OL,8,FGarfield Street he was behaving
OL,9,Ferratically, swearing and slurring his
OL,10,Fwords.
OL,12,FIn a separate incident, he was
OL,13,Farrested again on August 1 for a
OL,14,Fdrunken attack on a neighbour.
OL,16,FThe court heard he knocked on the
OL,17,Fvictim's door and asked to use his
OL,18,Fphone, lashing out and punching him in
OL,19,Fthe face when the request was denied.
