OL,7,FHurre admitted a charge of common
OL,8,Fassault in connection with that
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,FDefence solicitor Andrew Russell
OL,12,Fsuggested his client suffers from post-
OL,13,Ftraumatic distress related to his life
OL,14,Fin Somalia.
OL,16,FHe insisted that Hurre disputes making
OL,17,Fany claims to be the Prophet Muhammad
OL,18,For threatening to get a knife.
