OL,11,F"There is no doubt that he's a very
OL,12,Fenergetic character and acted in a
OL,13,Fmanner that caused distress to members
OL,14,Fof the public."
OL,16,FMr Russell also argued that Hurre
OL,17,Fassaulted his neighbour as part of "a
OL,18,Fconflict about how they were
OL,19,Fconducting their lives within the
OL,20,FMuslim faith".
